name: CoreAPI Run_TileBlackout
description: API to access results of Run_TileBlackout Details.
about:
Description

Run_TileBlackout maintains the list of the tiles to set them as blackout tiles.

API Run_TileBlackout is the Planet 9 API to access the API of the Blackout tiles list and the operations performed on them.

You can use API Run_TileBlackout in your app to change the status of the app as a blackout tile and to read the available app tiles set as"Blackout tile".

Every user must have the right roles (permissions) and authentication that enable access to the API Run_TileBlackout.

Operations Performed

Get

Get the selected application tile and tile group details.
